{"tid":1117096,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"CIA稱確認華為接受中國國家安全機構資金","createTime":"2019-04-20T12:30:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-20T13:59:12.000Z","uid":39464,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4136a5a42e1db249f9a186b2ecce05512217d69a","tid":1117096,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T12:30:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://scd.cn.rfi.fr/sites/chinese.filesrfi/imagecache/rfi_16x9_1024_578/sites/images.rfi.fr/files/aefimagesnew/aef_image/2019-04-11t145111z_446828772_rc1de2c1a310_rtrmadp_3_huawei-tech-security.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fscd.cn.rfi.fr%2Fsites%2Fchinese.filesrfi%2Fimagecache%2Frfi_16x9_1024_578%2Fsites%2Fimages.rfi.fr%2Ffiles%2Faefimagesnew%2Faef_image%2F2019-04-11t145111z_446828772_rc1de2c1a310_rtrmadp_3_huawei-tech-security.jpg&h=964bb79e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據英國泰晤士報本周六的消息，美國中央情報局認為，已經掌握證據，確認華為公司接受中國國家安全機構的資金，但該報並沒有引述這一消息的來源。<br />\n<br />\n泰晤士報報道稱，根據美國情報部門的消息，華為這一電信巨頭的資金來源當中，包括但並不僅限於中國軍隊，中國國家安全委員會，以及另外一個中國情報機構。<br />\n<br />\n美國通過五眼與英國，澳大利亞，加拿大，新西蘭四國進行情報機構聯盟合作，指控華為是中國政府的情報機構，並給歐洲盟國施壓，要求在開發5G市場時，排除華為。華為方面則表示，&ldquo;不對沒有任何證據，從匿名消息源產生的指控，做任何評價&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n泰晤士報表示，以上認為華為收到了中國多個情報單位的資金的消息，由美國中情局轉達給英國情報機構，而英國目前正在對其境內鋪設5G網絡進行最終收尾性質的廣域調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://trad.cn.rfi.fr/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20190420-%E7%BE%8E%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E6%83%85%E5%A0%B1%E5%B1%80%E7%A8%B1%E7%A2%BA%E8%AA%8D%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%A9%9F%E6%A7%8B%E8%B3%87%E9%87%91\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftrad.cn.rfi.fr%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F20190420-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E6%2583%2585%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%25B1%2580%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25AA%258D%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%258E%25A5%25E5%258F%2597%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%25A7%258B%25E8%25B3%2587%25E9%2587%2591&d=pT82QRnJ%2FvP0AhTzSnQTAnf7N2ZoUQ5IAXdO3fO0pAc%3D&h=aa5cf3dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://trad.cn.rfi.fr/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20190420-%E7%BE%8E%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E6%83%85%E5%A0%B1%E5%B1%80%E7%A8%B1%E7%A2%BA%E8%AA%8D%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%A9%9F%E6%A7%8B%E8%B3%87%E9%87%91</a>"},{"pid":"bf54276133c7331b849928f0eb885369aae92450","tid":1117096,"uid":182180,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T13:31:31.000Z","msg":"估都估到<br />\n唔係點用錢撻人做蝕本生意"},{"pid":"fc12fa5e01af9cb10e07d61def923bdca034dc43","tid":1117096,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T13:37:24.000Z","msg":"普通公司玩到封人網咁大支野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"756e2d4fa18fe7c2a05b3f4c4bb4fa0c4c5821ef","tid":1117096,"uid":182499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf54276133c7331b849928f0eb885369aae92450","tid":1117096,"uid":182180,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T13:31:31.000Z","msg":"估都估到<br />\n唔係點用錢撻人做蝕本生意"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T13:39:10.000Z","msg":"係人都估到 最緊要有證據<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3222aa825fe0d1973beaed42326e6e639571982e","tid":1117096,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T13:40:25.000Z","msg":"醒既開始醒"},{"pid":"c8d485be0ea2ce7bbfe98f671490d3e43a564bae","tid":1117096,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T13:42:07.000Z","msg":"弱智都知啦"},{"pid":"fa35e529547d538d9196ff04c4c69be1364414ca","tid":1117096,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T13:42:17.000Z","msg":"其實蝗係扮科技落後 <br />\n佢地偷資料科技係世界級"},{"pid":"63689a35616c5f74cc75498538f01b5f721bc193","tid":1117096,"uid":12628,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T13:43:40.000Z","msg":"屎為幾時都咁識做架啦<img src=\"/